SELECT project_name, task_name, MAX(TIMESTAMPDIFF(DAY, task_due_date, timeline_date)) AS max_delay_days FROM projects JOIN tasks ON projects.project_id = tasks.project_id JOIN timelines ON tasks.task_id = timelines.task_id GROUP BY project_name, task_name ORDER BY max_delay_days DESC;

SELECT project_name, timeline_date, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY project_name ORDER BY timeline_date) AS timeline_sequence FROM projects JOIN timelines ON projects.project_id = timelines.project_id;

SELECT project_name, task_name, timeline_date FROM projects JOIN tasks ON projects.project_id = tasks.project_id JOIN timelines ON tasks.task_id = timelines.task_id WHERE project_name LIKE 'Pro%' AND task_name LIKE 'Task%' AND timeline_date < '2023-01-01';
